# Generated file. It is a single line of roughly 1.9 MB, so formatting it would
# explode it into millions of lines and destroy every future diff.
ItemData.lua

# Vendored Ace3 externals. Not ours to format. These are also gitignored, which
# stylua honours on its own, but relying on that is too subtle to trust.
Libs/

# Generated by scripts/locales.py, which is the sole owner of their layout: one
# entry per line, sorted, untranslated keys commented out. stylua would wrap the
# long ones onto a second line, and then the two tools would fight over every
# run. One line per key is also what makes a translator's diff readable.
Locales/
